{
  "info": {
    "name": "Monitour API",
    "description": "Complete API collection for Monitour – Smart Operations, Surveillance & Workforce Management Platform.\n\n## Quick Start\n1. Set the `baseUrl` variable to `http://localhost:8000` (or your deployed API origin).\n2. Run **Login (Admin)** or **Login (Manager)** – the `accessToken` variable is set automatically.\n3. Authenticated requests use the collection Bearer token.\n\n## OpenAPI (keep in sync)\nIn Postman: **Import → Link** → `{{baseUrl}}/openapi.json` to merge the latest paths from the running server.\n\n## WesenseU & verification\nRoom verification (`POST /verification/task/{task_id}`) queues **Celery**; the worker downloads stored image URLs and POSTs **multipart** to WesenseU with optional **`benchmark_image_url`** and **`room_category`**. Run **WesenseU** on port **8001** and a **Celery worker** for end-to-end AI callbacks.\n\n## Credentials (dev seed)\n| Role | Email | Password |\n|------|-------|----------|\n| Super Admin | admin@monitour.in | Admin@2026 |\n| Property Manager | manager@grandpalace.com | Manager@123 |\n| Dept Manager | hk_head@grandpalace.com | DeptHead@123 |\n| Employee | priya@grandpalace.com | Password@123 |",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl",     "value": "http://localhost:8000", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "apiBase",     "value": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1",    "type": "string" },
    { "key": "accessToken", "value": "",                       "type": "string" },
    { "key": "propertyId",  "value": "",                       "type": "string" },
    { "key": "employeeId",  "value": "",                       "type": "string" },
    { "key": "roomId",      "value": "",                       "type": "string" },
    { "key": "taskId",      "value": "",                       "type": "string" },
    { "key": "ticketId",    "value": "",                       "type": "string" },
    { "key": "itemId",      "value": "",                       "type": "string" },
    { "key": "departmentId", "value": "",                    "type": "string" }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{accessToken}}", "type": "string" }]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "🔐 Authentication",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login (Admin)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', body.access_token);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('propertyId', body.user.property_id || '');",
                  "  pm.test('Login successful', () => pm.expect(body.access_token).to.be.a('string'));",
                  "  console.log('Logged in as:', body.user.full_name, '|', body.user.role);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@monitour.in\",\n  \"password\": \"Admin@2026\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{apiBase}}/auth/login", "host": ["{{apiBase}}"], "path": ["auth", "login"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (Manager)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
